value.0: Thank you for releasing me from that horrid fate. I fear that it shall not last long though. Allow me to bless you with the light and grant you a reward for your aid.

The first shall be the reward of knowledge. All through out your trip to this place you have gained pieces of knowledge along the way. The guardians are those who have been inparted knowledge to help beings like you understand what is happening and why this island's fate is so dark.

You see in a time long forgotten, there was a great power. This power brought to this place a city, where locked with in it is an essense light none the world has ever seen. This knowledge was forgotten by most. Then the order of nine realized its location and being wise knew that no one not man, beast, or undead could weild its power. So they sent to this place a Magi by the time of Razim to guard it.

Forgive me as i said it was from a time long ago. But the effects upon the island are from many things. An ancient evil which came here looking for the entry into this city, A mad mage who over the centuries has lost his mind and purpose, and finally the lost Foci of a ritual to stop it all. 28 scattered to the winds..
To set things right the races must unite in the goal for such with all 28 pieces and 10 mages. Razim was wise when he broke things apart but equally unwise to have lost the pieces of the broken Foci.
